['DescriptionEspace Real Estate is proud to present this immaculate 5 bedroom plus maids villa located in the sought after community of Saheel in Arabia Ranches. This wonderfully finished villa offers a large downstairs bedroom with en-suite, large reception and dining room on the same flat level, good size kitchen with family room, 4 good sized bedrooms upstairs, maids room and has a big private landscaped garden. Arabian Ranches has such a welcoming community feel in a peaceful and quiet location which makes it the perfect place to bring up a family. This villa will be the perfect property for everyone seeking a place that they can call home.
